126
00:05:48,060 --> 00:05:49,308
Scott: Now, hold on, hold on.

127
00:05:49,610 --> 00:05:53,099
Scott: I knew that you would go there because that is also the first thing I thought of.

128
00:05:53,160 --> 00:05:57,989
Rym: And I knew because of the way you phrased this that you were leading me there so that you could then redirect.

129
00:05:58,009 --> 00:05:59,400
Rym: So now I'm waiting for your redirect.

130
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:00,223
