131
00:06:00,263 --> 00:06:03,280
Scott: So you are correct and I 100% agree with you.

132
00:06:03,380 --> 00:06:07,139
Scott: If you're following someone, you don't actually want to see their tweets, just fucking unfollow them.

133
00:06:07,341 --> 00:06:10,840
