00:37:45,490 --> 00:37:53,270
Scott: So, you know, there's not really much I can upgrade other than getting some like monster servers or something else you can do, right?

713
00:37:53,330 --> 00:37:59,830
Scott: And this is what Vimeo actually does, is when they need to encode, when you send your video upload to Vimeo to get encoded, right?

714
00:38:00,071 --> 00:38:06,750
Scott: They send your video to all these Amazon instances that just spring up, encode your video, and then shut down, right?

