00:38:24,651 --> 00:38:32,310
Scott: And you got some ridiculously powerful machine to do the encoding, which costs a lot of money, but you're only using it for what, five minutes?

718
00:38:33,311 --> 00:38:38,530
Scott: So, you only paid like a dollar to use that machine for five minutes maybe, right?

719
00:38:38,710 --> 00:38:43,650
Scott: And you can actually, you know, if it saves you a lot of time, that's fucking worth it, right?

