728
00:39:13,461 --> 00:39:15,970
Rym: and then on video, like we don't like to hold microphones.

729
00:39:16,510 --> 00:39:19,190
Scott: Yeah, holding microphones on video is only good in certain situations.

730
00:39:19,390 --> 00:39:27,010
Scott: Usually where, you know, if you're doing like a TV show, like where you're a sitcom, you don't want to see anything on the screen, right?

731
00:39:27,111 --> 00:39:28,801
Scott: So you need to have a boom guy, right?

732
00:39:28,862 --> 00:39:30,130
Scott: Holding the microphone up above.

733
00:39:30,350 --> 00:39:32,009
Rym: Or a bunch of lavaliers, a lot of ways you can do it.

734
00:39:32,070 --> 00:39:35,070
