946
00:49:52,934 --> 00:49:53,725
Rym: They actually, no.

947
00:49:54,290 --> 00:50:03,970
Rym: So, when you buy their microphone, then you tell it what kind of wireless system you're going to use with it, and then they make it custom for that system.

948
00:50:04,751 --> 00:50:05,890
Rym: The connectors are all different.

949
00:50:05,990 --> 00:50:06,727
Rym: It's not just XLR.

950
00:50:06,870 --> 00:50:08,510
Scott: Why wouldn't they make an interchangeable connector?

951
00:50:08,630 --> 00:50:16,890
