1121
00:59:00,382 --> 00:59:02,950
Scott: You'll have to stop, change the battery, and start again.

1122
00:59:03,712 --> 00:59:05,550
Scott: Even if your memory card is gigantic, no good.

1123
00:59:05,650 --> 00:59:09,130
Rym: My camcorder has a special battery that's basically just an interface to the battery ports.

1124
00:59:09,610 --> 00:59:13,130
