Scott: And that made me think, "Aha, it is exactly the same as the GH3, isn't

1158
01:01:08,670 --> 01:01:08,710
Scott: it?".

1159
01:01:08,710 --> 01:01:09,648
Scott: And they're trying to bullshit me.

1160
01:01:10,370 --> 01:01:13,568
Scott: So, then I found another camera store in the city and they had the AC8.

