Scott: And I was in the store and I'm like, "Let me plug this into my camera before I buy it from you.

1164
01:01:22,250 --> 01:01:24,059
Scott: If my camera explodes, that's on me.

1165
01:01:24,139 --> 01:01:25,466
Scott: I'll just get the warranty or whatever.

1166
01:01:25,647 --> 01:01:26,310
Scott: I'll find a way.

1167
01:01:26,993 --> 01:01:28,207
Scott: If it doesn't explode, I'm buying

1168
01:01:28,247 --> 01:01:28,368
Scott: this.".

1169
01:01:28,772 --> 01:01:30,685
Scott: And of course, it didn't explode.

1170
01:01:30,705 --> 01:01:31,390
Scott: It totally worked.

1171
01:01:31,796 --> 01:01:32,070
Rym: Alright.

